19:38.450 --> 19:39.010
Ayo.

19:39.680 --> 19:40.320
Makanlah sesuap.

19:41.150 --> 19:41.750
Ayo.

19:42.510 --> 19:43.190
Buka mulut.

19:44.430 --> 19:45.030
Buka mulut.

19:45.750 --> 19:46.430
Makanlah sesuap.

